OpenSPARC_T1_original/
======================

Sun Microsystems' original, unmodified 2006 OpenSPARC T1 "niagara" Legion
release. Contains originating content from /images/legion/src/config,
extracted from OpenSPARCT1_Arch.1.5.tar.bz2 -- Sun's official OpenSPARC T1
architecture release archive.

Kept exactly as shipped, including its own Makefile/Makefile.master and
mixed source+blob layout (niagara/*.pdesc, *.hdesc, *.conf, *-md.bin,
*-hv.bin). This is the ground-truth reference everything else in this
repo is validated against -- see ../../README (bin/README): the
OpenSPARC_T1_rebuild config proves our own mdgen toolchain reproduces
these binaries byte-for-byte.
